room_title: Escape room "Backstage at the Magic Show" by Escape Haus in San Marcos
room_description: You just started your dream job as a magician's assistant. Tonight is his big show and he's depending on you to set up the stage. As you enter the Prop Room, the door slams shut...and locks behind you. The show starts in an hour. Your dream job is on the line. The crowd is taking their seats. Will you find your way out in time?
